  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Like the waves flow towards the shore,</l>
            <l>so do the minutes come to an end</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>Every place we have been changes,</l>
            <l>When you are working hard for something progress comes within time.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Life begins with Nativity</l>
            <l>small steps lead to success,</l>
            <l>time allows to make progress.</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>time has different aspects, life and progress</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Time is more <choice><orig>powerfull</orig><reg>powerful</reg></choice> than any beauty</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>It lets beauty fade when you are getting old</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>Death is part of the living <choice><orig>cyrcle</orig><reg>circle</reg></choice>,</l>
            <l>And nothing is certain except for death.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>And yet to later times I hope my poem still exists,</l>
            <l><choice><orig>It's</orig><reg>It</reg></choice> does not change, despite the changes because of time.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
